i\":\"http://p1.music.126.net/lMLK9H8GRI68IllBvhQEEA==/109951170699827602.jpg\",\"or\":\"orpheus://nm/artist/home?id=31211&type=artist\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Giorgio Tuinfort\"}]}\n[00:12.950]Light 'em up, light 'em up\n[00:14.880]Tell me where you are, tell me where you are\n[00:19.210]The summer nights, the bright lights\n[00:21.330]And the shooting stars, they break my heart\n[00:24.510]\n[00:24.950]I'm Calling you now, but you're not picking up\n[00:28.120]Your shadow‘s so close if you are still in love\n[00:32.100]Then light a match, light a match\n[00:34.260]Baby, in the dark, show me where you are\n[00:37.760]\n[00:39.410]Oh, love\n[00:41.020]How I miss you every single day\n[00:43.020]When I see you on those streets\n[00:45.790]Oh, love\n[00:47.490]Tell me there's a river I can swim that will bring you back to me\n[00:52.080]Cause I don't know how to love someone else\n[00:55.320]I don't know how to forget your face\n[00:58.680]Oh, love\n[01:00.320]God, I miss you every single day and now you're so far away\n[01:09.660]So far away\n[01:11.040]\n[01:17.180]It's breaking me, I'm losing you\n[01:19.290]We were far from perfect\n[01:21.220]But we were worth it\n[01:23.600]Too many fights, and we cried\n[01:25.680]But never said we're sorry\n[01:27.600]Stop saying you love me\n[01:29.150]\n[01:29.170]You're calling me now, but I can't pick up\n[01:32.510]Your shadow's too close, and I'm still in love\n[01:36.120]The summer's over now\n[01:37.620]But somehow it still breaks my heart\n[01:40.200]We could have had the stars, oh\n[01:43.290]\n[01:43.900]Oh, love\n[01:45.410]How I miss you every single day\n[01:47.430]When I see you on those streets\n[01:50.260]Oh, love\n[01:50.300]Tell me there's a river I can swim that will bring you back to me\n[01:56.540]Cause I don't know how to love someone else\n[01:59.740]I don't know how to forget your face\n[02:03.170]Oh, love\n[02:04.730]God, I miss you every single day and now you're so far away\n[02:08.990]\n[02:13.940]So far away\n[02:20.560]So far away, oh\n[02:26.870]So far away\n[02:33.360]So far away\n[02:34.810]\n[02:35.490]Oh, love\n[02:37.040]How I miss you every single day\n[02:39.030]When I see you on those streets\n[02:41.860]Oh, love\n[02:43.440]Tell me there's a river I can swim that will bring you back to me\n[02:48.010]Cause I don't know how to love someone else\n[02:51.310]I don't know how to forget your face\n[02:54.800]Oh, love\n[02:56.340]God, I miss you every single day when you're so far away\n"},"klyric":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"tlyric":{"version":21,"lyric":"[00:12.950]点燃一束光，照亮它们\n[00:14.880]告诉我你身在何处 身在何处\n[00:19.210]仲夏夜晚 烛光摇曳\n[00:21.330]流星划过夜空 也伤透了我的心\n[00:24.510]\n[00:24.950]现在我拨通你的电话 但你不会再接\n[00:28.120]你的身影近在咫尺 却远在天涯\n[00:32.100]划亮一根火柴 照亮黑夜\n[00:34.260]宝贝告诉我 黑夜之中你在哪里\n[00:37.760]\n[00:39.410]噢 挚爱\n[00:41.020]我每日每夜无时无刻不想念着你\n[00:43.020]走在街上看到每个人都觉得是你的身影\n[00:45.790]噢 挚爱\n[00:47.490]告诉我我还有计可施 还有机会让你回心转意\n[00:52.080]因为我真的不知道如何再去爱上别人\n[00:55.320]我不知道该如何忘掉你的容颜\n[00:58.680]噢 挚爱\n[01:00.320]我对你朝思暮想 如今你遥不可及\n[01:09.660]如此遥不可及\n[01:11.040]\n[01:17.180]失去你我也痛彻心扉\n[01:19.290]我们虽不是完美恋人\n[01:21.220]但这一切的经历都值得\n[01:23.600]我们争吵过 也哭红过双眼\n[01:25.680]但我们都从未说过抱歉\n[01:27.600]别告诉我你对我还存有爱意\n[01:29.150]\n[01:29.170]你试图联系我 但我不能有任何回应\n[01:32.510]你的身影还是如此清晰 我也依然爱着你\n[01:36.120]夏天已经结束\n[01:37.620]不知怎么仍然刺痛我的心\n\n[01:40.200]我们本可以拥有灿烂星河\n[01:43.290]\n[01:43.900]噢 挚爱\n[01:45.410]我每日每夜无时无刻不想念着你\n[01:47.430]走在街上看到每个人都觉得是你的身影\n[01:50.260]噢 挚爱\n[01:50.300]告诉我我还有计可施 还有机会让你回心转意\n[01:56.540]因为我真的不知道如何再去爱上别人\n[01:59.740]我不知道该如何忘掉你的容颜\n[02:03.170]噢 挚爱\n[02:04.730]我对你朝思暮想 如今你遥不可及\n[02:08.990]\n[02:13.940]如此遥不可及\n[02:20.560]如此遥不可及\n[02:26.870]如此遥不可及\n[02:33.360]如此遥不可及\n[02:34.810]\n[02:35.490]噢 挚爱\n[02:37.040]我每日每夜无时无刻不想念着你\n[02:39.030]走在街上看到每个人都觉得是你的身影\n[02:41.860]噢 挚爱\n[02:43.440]告诉我我还有计可施 还有机会让你回心转意\n[02:48.010]因为我真的不知道如何再去爱上别人\n[02:51.310]我不知道该如何忘掉你的容颜\n[02:54.800]噢 挚爱\n[02:56.340]我对你朝思暮想 如今你遥不可及"},"romalrc":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"yrc":{"version":78,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"